    "summary": "Repair open PR #88681 in place by rebasing/resolving conflicts against current main and keeping the runtime plugin startup diagnostic change narrow. The repaired branch should preserve @alexzhu0's authorship and only adjust the contributor branch enough to pass exact-head review and validation.",
    "pr_title": "Make runtime plugin startup stalls name in-flight plugins",
    "pr_body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nRepairs #88681 so runtime-plugin startup stalls include attempted, completed, and in-flight plugin IDs in the relevant embedded-agent and isolated-cron timeout diagnostics.\n\n## Why This Change Was Made\n\nThe existing contributor branch is useful and maintainer-modifiable, but preflight reports it is dirty against current `main`. Clownfish should rebase/resolve conflicts narrowly instead of replacing the work.\n\n## User Impact\n\nOperators investigating `runtime-plugins` startup stalls get actionable plugin IDs instead of a coarse phase name.\n\n## Evidence\n\n- Source PR: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/pull/88681 by @alexzhu0\n- Related tracker: #87327\n- Preserve contributor credit and keep the repaired diff scoped to runtime plugin load progress and cron/embedded-agent timeout reporting.\n- Run focused Vitest files for plugin loader/runtime plugin/cron diagnostics, then `pnpm check:changed`.\n\nNo `CHANGELOG.md` edit: release generation owns changelog updates.",
    "likely_files": [
      "src/plugins/loader.ts",
      "src/plugins/runtime/load-diagnostics.ts",
      "src/plugins/loader.test.ts",
      "src/agents/runtime-plugins.ts",
      "src/agents/runtime-plugins.test.ts",
      "src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run.ts",
      "src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run/params.ts",
      "src/cron/isolated-agent/run.ts",
      "src/cron/isolated-agent/run.runtime-plugins.test.ts",
      "src/cron/service/execution-errors.ts",
      "src/cron/service/execution-errors.test.ts",
      "src/cron/service/timer.regression.test.ts",
      "src/cron/types.ts"
    ],
    "validation_commands": [
      "node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/plugins/loader.test.ts src/agents/runtime-plugins.test.ts src/cron/isolated-agent/run.runtime-plugins.test.ts src/cron/service/execution-errors.test.ts src/cron/service/timer.regression.test.ts",
      "pnpm check:changed"
    ],
